snippet.title: Galaxy 3D Space Defender ::FIRST FOOTAGE KNOWN TO MAN::
snippet.description:
Pardon the toaster mic, but, my good pal Evan purchased this undergrad college kiddo's project to help buy them a cup of fucking ramen (probably) so happy Hanukkah Christmas cheer season. It came with no instructions, and if they were written, they're in Sanskrit or some shit because I can't read them. I had no clue what I was doing. God Bless.
---
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN, I AM PROUD TO PRESENT: Galaxy 3D Space Defender
